  <brief_title>Pain After PRP Revascularization and Endodontic Treatment of Non-vital Mandibular Molars With Apical Periodontitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Post-operative Pain Following Platelet Rich Plasma (PRP) Revascularization Versus Conventional Endodontic Treatment of Non-vital Mature Mandibular Molars With Chronic Peri-apical Periodontitis</official_title>
